metadata.name: Fast and Furious
metadata.description:
This is a picture captured from Kerala,India,Farmers conduct such races as part of tradition,winning this race is a prestige for them,many well trained riders ride on such bulls.
It was my first time watching such a race,I went with my friends,I had fear of getting hit by bulls,but with confidence of having a 500mm lens I stood there and took this Photo.
Bulls run towards us with immense speed splashing the mud.
This image is one of the Best which I got on that day.
